<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Track the Fox: OSINT Challenge Series</h1>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Project Overview</h2>
            <p>Track the Fox is an exciting new OSINT (Open Source Intelligence) challenge series designed to test and improve participants' investigative skills. Inspired by platforms like Hack The Box, we aim to create engaging, realistic scenarios that push the boundaries of open-source intelligence gathering.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Content Planning</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><span class="highlight">Bi-weekly challenges</span> (alternating between team members)</li>
                <li><span class="highlight">5 initial challenges</span> to launch the series</li>
                <li>Each challenge to include:
                    <ul>
                        <li>Detailed backstory</li>
                        <li>Multiple clues across various platforms</li>
                        <li>Technical elements (e.g., metadata analysis, network traffic investigation)</li>
                        <li>Red herrings to increase difficulty</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Scoring system based on accuracy, speed, and technique</li>
                <li>Community forum for discussions and hints</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Challenge Ideas</h2>
            <ol>
                <li><strong class="highlight">The Encrypted Enigma</strong>: Uncover a missing researcher's discovery through encrypted blog posts, hidden metadata, and network analysis.</li>
                <li><strong class="highlight">The Vanishing Vlogger</strong>: Track down a missing travel vlogger using social media clues and geolocation techniques.</li>
                <li><strong class="highlight">Corporate Crypto Conundrum</strong>: Investigate a suspicious new cryptocurrency and the company behind it.</li>
                <li><strong class="highlight">The Sound of Secrets</strong>: Decode hidden messages in audio files using advanced audio analysis.</li>
                <li><strong class="highlight">Digital Breadcrumbs</strong>: Connect seemingly unrelated social media accounts to a single individual.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Technical Requirements</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Web hosting for challenge materials</li>
                <li>Secure file storage for downloadable content</li>
                <li>Forum or Discord server for community interaction</li>
                <li>Submission system for challenge solutions</li>
                <li>Leaderboard to track participant progress</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Next Steps</h2>
            <ol>
                <li>Finalize challenge details for "The Encrypted Enigma"</li>
                <li>Set up web hosting and community platforms</li>
                <li>Create promotional materials for launch</li>
                <li>Recruit beta testers to validate challenge difficulty</li>
                <li>Establish a release schedule for the first five challenges</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
